  "title": "Structural Accumulation and Detection",
  "concept": "Physical structures change continuously through repeated activity, but become measurable only when enough material has accumulated—different processes build at different rates, reaching detectability at different times.",
  "interactiveId": "2b671bfe-d164-4814-b1b8-c42055f298a3",
  "sourcePieceId": "24105499-7103-437c-b231-d40bdaae5bb1",
  "publishedAt": 1778033267652,
  "voiceScore": 88,
  "qualityFlag": "low",
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Structural Accumulation and Detection</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --synaptic: #c9a227;\n    --tract: #1a6b62;\n    --cortical: #8b7355;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .control-group {\n    margin-bottom: 32px;\n  }\n  .control {\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .control label {\n    display: block;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .slider-row {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 12px;\n  }\n  .slider-row input[type=range] {\n    flex: 1;\n    accent-color: var(--tract);\n    min-width: 100px;\n  }\n  .slider-row output {\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    min-width: 4ch;\n    text-align: right;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .layers {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 24px;\n    margin: 24px 0;\n  }\n  .layer {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 14px;\n  }\n  .layer-header {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: baseline;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n  .layer-name {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .layer-status {\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n  }\n  .layer-status.detectable {\n    color: var(--fg);\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  .bar-container {\n    position: relative;\n    height: 32px;\n    background: var(--line);\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .bar-fill {\n    height: 100%;\n    transition: width 200ms ease-out;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .layer[data-type=\"synaptic\"] .bar-fill { background: var(--synaptic); }\n  .layer[data-type=\"tract\"] .bar-fill { background: var(--tract); }\n  .layer[data-type=\"cortical\"] .bar-fill { background: var(--cortical); }\n  .threshold-marker {\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 40%;\n    top: 0;\n    bottom: 0;\n    width: 2px;\n    background: var(--fg);\n    opacity: 0.3;\n  }\n  .threshold-marker::after {\n    content: 'detection threshold';\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 6px;\n    top: 50%;\n    transform: translateY(-50%);\n    font-size: 0.65rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    background: #fff;\n    padding: 2px 4px;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n  .reading {\n    margin: 24px 0 6px;\n    padding: 12px 16px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .reading strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 480px) {\n    .threshold-marker::after {\n      font-size: 0.6rem;\n      padding: 1px 3px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Drag to increase activity frequency</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">Three types of structural change accumulate as activity repeats. Each builds at a different rate.</p>\n\n<div class=\"control-group\">\n  <div class=\"control\">\n    <label for=\"frequency\">Activity frequency:</label>\n    <div class=\"slider-row\">\n      <input id=\"frequency\" type=\"range\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" step=\"1\" aria-describedby=\"freq-out\">\n      <output id=\"freq-out\" for=\"frequency\">0</output>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"layers\">\n  <div class=\"layer\" data-type=\"synaptic\">\n    <div class=\"layer-header\">\n      <span class=\"layer-name\">Connection strength</span>\n      <span class=\"layer-status\" id=\"status-synaptic\">0% built</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"bar-container\">\n      <div class=\"bar-fill\" id=\"bar-synaptic\" style=\"width: 0%;\"></div>\n      <div class=\"threshold-marker\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"layer\" data-type=\"tract\">\n    <div class=\"layer-header\">\n      <span class=\"layer-name\">Pathway organization</span>\n      <span class=\"layer-status\" id=\"status-tract\">0% built</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"bar-container\">\n      <div class=\"bar-fill\" id=\"bar-tract\" style=\"width: 0%;\"></div>\n      <div class=\"threshold-marker\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"layer\" data-type=\"cortical\">\n    <div class=\"layer-header\">\n      <span class=\"layer-name\">Regional expansion</span>\n      <span class=\"layer-status\" id=\"status-cortical\">0% built</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"bar-container\">\n      <div class=\"bar-fill\" id=\"bar-cortical\" style=\"width: 0%;\"></div>\n      <div class=\"threshold-marker\"></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"reading\">\n  Measurable layers: <strong id=\"detectable\">none</strong>.\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">All three layers are accumulating material, but none has crossed the detection threshold yet.</p>\n\n<script>\n  (function () {\n    var slider = document.getElementById('frequency');\n    var freqOut = document.getElementById('freq-out');\n    var detectable = document.getElementById('detectable');\n    var caption = document.getElementById('caption');\n\n    var layers = {\n      synaptic: {\n        rate: 1.8,\n        bar: document.getElementById('bar-synaptic'),\n        status: document.getElementById('status-synaptic')\n      },\n      tract: {\n        rate: 0.7,\n        bar: document.getElementById('bar-tract'),\n        status: document.getElementById('status-tract')\n      },\n      cortical: {\n        rate: 0.35,\n        bar: document.getElementById('bar-cortical'),\n        status: document.getElementById('status-cortical')\n      }\n    };\n\n    var threshold = 40;\n\n    function update() {\n      var freq = +slider.value;\n      freqOut.textContent = freq;\n\n      var synapticAcc = Math.min(100, layers.synaptic.rate * freq);\n      var tractAcc = Math.min(100, layers.tract.rate * freq);\n      var corticalAcc = Math.min(100, layers.cortical.rate * freq);\n\n      layers.synaptic.bar.style.width = synapticAcc + '%';\n      layers.tract.bar.style.width = tractAcc + '%';\n      layers.cortical.bar.style.width = corticalAcc + '%';\n\n      var synapticDetectable = synapticAcc >= threshold;\n      var tractDetectable = tractAcc >= threshold;\n      var corticalDetectable = corticalAcc >= threshold;\n\n      if (synapticDetectable) {\n        layers.synaptic.status.textContent = 'measurable';\n        layers.synaptic.status.classList.add('detectable');\n      } else {\n        layers.synaptic.status.textContent = Math.round(synapticAcc) + '% built';\n        layers.synaptic.status.classList.remove('detectable');\n      }\n\n      if (tractDetectable) {\n        layers.tract.status.textContent = 'measurable';\n        layers.tract.status.classList.add('detectable');\n      } else {\n        layers.tract.status.textContent = Math.round(tractAcc) + '% built';\n        layers.tract.status.classList.remove('detectable');\n      }\n\n      if (corticalDetectable) {\n        layers.cortical.status.textContent = 'measurable';\n        layers.cortical.status.classList.add('detectable');\n      } else {\n        layers.cortical.status.textContent = Math.round(corticalAcc) + '% built';\n        layers.cortical.status.classList.remove('detectable');\n      }\n\n      var detected = [];\n      if (synapticDetectable) detected.push('connection strength');\n      if (tractDetectable) detected.push('pathway organization');\n      if (corticalDetectable) detected.push('regional expansion');\n\n      if (detected.length === 0) {\n        detectable.textContent = 'none';\n        if (freq === 0) {\n          caption.textContent = 'All three layers are accumulating material, but none has crossed the detection threshold yet.';\n        } else {\n          caption.textContent = 'Material is building in all three layers, but your measurement tool cannot see any of them yet.';\n        }\n      } else if (detected.length === 1) {\n        detectable.textContent = detected[0];\n        if (detected[0] === 'connection strength') {\n          caption.textContent = 'Connection strength crossed first—it builds fastest. The other two layers are still accumulating below the detection line.';\n        } else if (detected[0] === 'pathway organization') {\n          caption.textContent = 'Pathway organization is now measurable. Connection strength crossed earlier; regional expansion is still below threshold.';\n        } else {\n          caption.textContent = 'Regional expansion just crossed. It took the longest to accumulate enough material to measure.';\n        }\n      } else if (detected.length === 2) {\n        detectable.textContent = detected[0] + ' and ' + detected[1];\n        if (!corticalDetectable) {\n          caption.textContent = 'Two layers measurable. Regional expansion is still accumulating—faster processes show up sooner.';\n        } else {\n          caption.textContent = 'Two of three crossed. Faster accumulation means earlier detection.';\n        }\n      } else {\n        detectable.textContent = 'all three';\n        caption.textContent = 'All three layers are measurable now. Connection strength crossed first, then pathway organization, finally regional expansion—same threshold, different build rates.';\n      }\n    }\n\n    slider.addEventListener('input', update);\n    update();\n  })();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
